data.description: Gorgeous 1.5 story home in a beautiful Master Planned Community, Harmony! This home was built by Highland Homes & offers such great, functional space. 4 Bedrooms, 3.5 Baths, Study & Gameroom, as well as oversized 2.5 Garage w/workbench area & storage! Open Floor plan-great for entertaining or spending time w/family. Kitchen has stainless appliances (incl. refrig); granite ctrs, ctr island w/seating & breakfast room. Living Room has stone gas fireplace. Tile floors flow seamlessly through most of first floor common areas. Study features wood flooring & a closet, so if you need a 5th bedroom, this is a good option! Gameroom, full bath & 4th bedroom upstairs, all other bedrooms down. Primary Bedroom is oversized. Primary Bath has large separate shower, oversized tub, dbl sinks & vanity area. Great walk in closet space in all bedrooms. High ceilings, upgraded lighting. Enclosed sunroom & covered patio w/new roof on pergola. Plumbed gas-line on back patio-grill stays. New Fence. NO FLOODING
